data.description: Newly-designed open plan three bedroom, two bath pool home complete with a large lanai showcasing a huge under-truss outdoor living area. Kitchen has all new high-end stainless steel appliances, undermount sink, new cabinets, garbage disposal, with expansive counter space. This beautiful home is situated on a large oversized lot on a low-traffic street with no restrictive HOA. The home has brand new quartz counters throughout, impressive triple and double sliders, a hard-wired security camera system with DVR, impact windows with storm shutters, new roof under warranty, new A/C, new pool equipment, new water softener, and many additional upgrades.
